&lt;p&gt;GMMH have an exciting opportunity to recruit Registered Mental Health Nurses within one of their services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maple House is a 6 bedded mixed sex Psychiatric Intensive Care Unit (PICU) based on the same site as the Royal Bolton General Hospital, we have vacancies for qualified nurses in mental health, &lt;strong&gt;both experienced or newly qualified&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maple House is a busy PICU where staff show a high degree of motivation and commitment to deliver excellent care. We have a substantial support package available to new starters and staff on the preceptorship pathway.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will show a strong interest in inpatient mental health services and demonstrate the GMMH Trust values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
